divs: sighting detailswhile driving home with a co-worker at approximately 8:10pm on april 12 2012 in lawrenceville\trenton nj part of rt 295 south right before the 195 intersection. we saw what looked like two bright neon blue oval type lights attached to some kind of object and it was traveling super fast - like a meteor falling to earth - the object became invisible while in our site (it did not travel below a tree line) - it just disappeared.
Summary: object with 2 bright blue neon lights movement similar to meteor
trends: There have been no other sightings in Lawrenceville
